text: RT @dklaidman: “Frankly I’m scared,” @BethCameron_DC said, that in the middle of a public health emergency like COVID-19, the CDC “isn’t at the table” and “is not out in front taking about this.” Sobering conversation on @SkullduggeryPod with @Isikoff. https://t.co/bNKaK1YL9h
